{"tid":58372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1月5號有筍工益各位巴絲打（2）","createTime":"2016-12-28T18:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T18:10:44.000Z","uid":22825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf20f9dc62bd00e27ae93ef47d793d3f02244151","tid":58372,"uid":22825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"事源：<br />\n有冇人知道1月5號尖嘴朗廷酒店有咩會議要搞？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/44717/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/44717/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n話說當日就冇巴絲打可以搵到到底1月5好尖沙嘴朗廷酒店會議廳搞咩嘢，而且請人撐場呢種做法其實都唔係土共特有，所以最後都不了了之，只有本人繼續留意下有冇相關新聞。<br />\n<br />\n之但係今日小弟居然又發現左新post：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/29/020515_0d67a199d05b3f2095a64a0267b484c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F29%2F020515_0d67a199d05b3f2095a64a0267b484c6.jpg&h=12824020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次講明要識國語，本人認為舉辦者既目的都呼之欲出啦。可惜本人係網上都係搵唔到相關活動，所以唯有做一次標題黨，等更多巴絲見到，可能當中會有知情者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb89d4184c72086551a2763d062a2b6b0c0c79b9","tid":58372,"uid":22825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"自己pish"}]}